title: Watch: Chris Hemsworth makes own superhero video
text:
Los Angeles: Chris Hemsworth, best known for playing the mighty Thor, has made his own superhero video.
  A video posted by Chris Hemsworth (@chrishemsworth) onOct 21, 2015 at 12:28pm PDT
The 15-second video was shared on Instagram on Wednesday featuring some of his friends from his native Australia, acting out a 'Superman' movie moment, reports people.com.
In the video, Hemsworth and a friend are driving as another friend flies up to the window asking for some quick directions and they all have a laugh at the stunt.
